Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到花该是件多高兴的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的不是送花的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 谁送花会比较高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦 是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸红害羞 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯的那个初夏的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也照旧到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是水星大潮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去参加凤尾舟协会的会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚应该就能回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天暖洋洋的呢 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.19,0:01:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是亚利亚公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是本大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在长靴小路等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用超快的速度给我赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用超快的速度哦 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}总觉得有点害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}哎呀 你丈夫送给你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}今天一天都很紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}不知道我能不能收到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:25.28,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 伯克洛节上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸前戴着红玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是伯克洛节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子 你太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生 拉头发禁止啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不是鬓子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？谁叫你的鬓角这么多破绽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好多玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装了整整一筐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我是想啊…送给艾莉西亚小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天是伯克洛节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 绝佳的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今天可是男人给爱慕之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送上一朵玫瑰的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那已经不止一朵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本大爷对艾莉西亚小姐的崇高的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只用一朵花来表达怎么够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有把全城的玫瑰都买下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能表达我无限的爱意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白吗 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生一个人拿不了这么多花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才叫我来帮忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该觉得光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小的女孩们也都戴着花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝也收到玫瑰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 是面包屋的叔叔送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是友情玫瑰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 难道这也是友情玫瑰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你说那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是晓先生要送给艾莉西亚前辈的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为那是灯里前辈从不同的人那里收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为雅典娜前辈一大早就收到了一堆玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司的后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 她好像有很多小孩子的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝也送给雅典娜前辈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不送友情玫瑰主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算我送玫瑰给她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只不过是多了一朵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对雅典娜前辈来说 没有什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得雅典娜前辈会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给她的话 她会高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉凉的石板路好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水面上倒映着天空 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晾晒的衣物 建筑物的格子窗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 还有浮岛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就像在镜子之国里一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边 让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 哥斯拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准叫我哥斯拉 你这个马尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准叫我马尾男 你这只哥斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尾男马尾男马尾男马尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥斯拉哥斯拉哥斯拉哥斯拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}马尾男马尾男马尾男马尾男…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华也收到玫瑰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是阿鲁送的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是阿鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊 是我要送给艾莉西亚前辈的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说马尾男…那些玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都要送给艾莉西亚前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有一朵花是无法展现我的心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 灯里 艾莉西亚前辈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她去参加凤尾舟协会的会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尾男 我会抢先把花送给艾莉西亚前辈的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 蓝华…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭哥斯拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 本大爷就要用数量压倒一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿晓～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 灯里 你好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好多玫瑰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这些几乎都是送给晃前辈的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬屋的晃小姐似乎很受女孩子欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年我都要给她投递很多玫瑰的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是晃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 这是阿晓你托我买的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没给我钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 先欠着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你要拒绝老朋友的请求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是阿晓 你上次借的和上上次借的都还…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候我把脆脆冰中奖的雪糕棒给了你对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别告诉我你不记得这个恩情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这么久以前的事情了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要中奖的雪糕棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭得满地打滚的那个是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想我把那件事添油加醋地告诉鬓子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里小姐 我还要干活 先走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 请加油工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要继续买吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要表达本大爷的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点玫瑰远远不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你就不能再便宜点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便宜不了就是便宜不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀你就再便宜一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}我可是全都买光哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯克洛节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯克洛到底是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯克洛是花蕾的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你讲讲伯克洛节的由来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伯克洛节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男性无论老少都会给爱慕的人送上一朵红玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个节日的传统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个传统的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是数百年前发生在地球上的真实故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个爱上了高贵姑娘的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下级贵族青年的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个青年为了向姑娘的父亲展示自己的诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就自告奋勇地上了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不幸的青年在战斗中受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终体力不支而倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他倒下的地方恰好是一片白玫瑰花丛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青年拼尽最后一丝气力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘下一朵玫瑰交给了战友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘收到被青年的鲜血染红的白玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知了自己的爱人已经战死的噩耗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是个悲伤的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也很浪漫不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红玫瑰象征着永恒的爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还有这样一个故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人真可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你砍完价了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 本大爷完胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的很不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事的男女主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经在数百年前过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但青年的爱仍旧化作红色玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直流传到了今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 凤尾舟协会的会议刚刚结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢了一步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来 在亚利亚公司门前等会比较快吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老家在浮岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一直在那里待到昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正准备回地下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水星大潮的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐的公司都放假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是开店歇业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且今天还是伯克洛节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那朵玫瑰是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…这是我自己买来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想送给艾莉西亚前辈的玫瑰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…我说这是别人送的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁会是什么样的表情呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐对宝石有兴趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝石？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是怎么突然想起问这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为「玫瑰之瞳」的宝石原石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地下世界偶尔能挖到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玫瑰之瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过竟然借玫瑰的话题送我宝石原石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…莫非这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…到底是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 蓝华 阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊 灯里小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 晓君也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 阿鲁 好久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 你见到艾莉西亚前辈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 这是怎么回事啊 晓君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多玫瑰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是本大爷为了表达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}比大海还要深沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}比浮岛还要高远的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}对艾莉西亚小姐的爱意才买下的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁送我这块石头的含义…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是热情的气候调节员 晓君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 晃前辈好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我见到伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他投递了好多送给晃前辈的玫瑰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…每年都是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐 你发烧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸好红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我没什么问题啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？刚才？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 还是先帮我找艾莉西亚前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝…蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 快走快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这样就做好万全的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就是送玫瑰的练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子啊 拜托你演一下艾莉西亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 艾莉西亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的…心…心…心…心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习就这么紧张怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你的表情好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 而且你演的艾莉西亚小姐一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还挺有自信的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看了艾莉西亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演得不像还这么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那见到真人会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会怎么样我也无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才拜托你陪我练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们再来一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 艾莉西亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟协会的会议结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我正准备回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好多玫瑰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是工作关系上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从熟客和联络处那里收到了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这这这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的心…心…心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 灯里才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从晓君那里收到了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打扰你们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…艾 艾莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 亚利亚社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚小姐！Come back！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Back…back…back…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音 传不到那边了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个废柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铺满了整个水面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直 延伸到远处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像 很久以前那对恋人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,映照在人心中蔓延开来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人对另外一个人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那温柔又略带哀愁的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给每个人的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都带来了和煦的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人不可思议地换上笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色玫瑰的传说所施下的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊 蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐 关于刚才那个玫瑰之瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要稍加雕琢就会变得很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的宝石一定很适合蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边也有红色玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色五花肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}日语中五花肉与玫瑰有部分发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老头子的冷笑话 禁止…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是地球上流传已久的文字游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找到艾莉西亚前辈之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要陪着我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能传达给艾莉西亚前辈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那毫无根据的自信是从哪来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你陪了我一天的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次收到男孩子送的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:21:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一朵红玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说无论是男性还是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到花都会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送上一朵红玫瑰的伯克洛节
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛开在水星大潮的城市中的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那鲜艳的玫瑰红
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显得是那么的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是个小小的纪念日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐 能度过美好的一天真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色玫瑰的传说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是个悲伤的爱情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有点让人憧憬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 朴实的星光…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:02:01.83,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:14.81,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:29.86,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:42.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:48.98,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:56.59,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:04.10,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.63,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:14.41,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:02:01.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:14.81,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:29.86,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:42.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:48.98,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:56.59,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:04.10,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.63,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:14.41,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:56.02,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨が上がる 遠く空眺め 雲の切れ間探す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:07.90,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつもよりも 少し遠回り 海へ続く道を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}切りすぎた前髪 気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:20.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そのまま 駆け出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:27.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をかすめていく 風の色が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:32.69,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつか夏のはじまりを告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:38.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}大きく手を振って 深呼吸しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:44.54,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}この時間を抱きしめていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:49.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}明日もまた会えるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:56.02,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨过天晴 眺望遥远的天空 探寻云彩的缝隙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:23:07.90,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}绕过早已习惯的归途 向着通往大海的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.61,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}忘掉剪得过短的留海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:20.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}毫无顾忌地大胆前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:27.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}吹拂着面颊的海风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:32.69,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不知何时染上了初夏的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:38.93,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}用力挥挥手 来个深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:44.54,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}满心希望永远拥抱这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:49.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}明天 我们还会再见吗
